OL,7,FA considerable overhaul is needed to
OL,8,Fsecure the future of the Welsh
OL,9,Flanguage, according to an independent
OL,10,Freport into the Welsh Government's
OL,11,Fstrategy.
OL,13,FThe number of people speaking Welsh in
OL,14,Fso-called "heartland" communities is
OL,15,Fdeclining and there is a real concern
OL,16,Fin some quarters about the language
OL,17,Fdisappearing as a widely-spoken
OL,18,Fcommunity language.
