OL,5,Csignificance'
OL,7,FThe Commission for Welsh-speaking
OL,8,FCommunities has suggested 57
OL,9,Frecommendations to strengthen the
OL,10,FWelsh language in what is known as
OL,11,F"heartland" communities: those places
OL,12,Fwhere a significant number of people
OL,13,Fspeak Welsh.
OL,15,FOne of the most striking
OL,16,Frecommendations is for those
OL,17,Fcommunities to become "areas of higher
OL,18,Fdensity linguistic significance".
