OL,7,FThis would allow them to introduce
OL,8,Fpolicies which specifically address
OL,9,Fthe particular needs of those
OL,10,Fcommunities, and in doing so help make
OL,11,Fthe language more sustainable.
OL,13,FDr Simon Brooks, chair of the
OL,14,Fcommission, said of language decline:
OL,15,F"We know that this has happened in
OL,16,Fother countries - Scottish gaelic for
OL,17,Fexample - we don't want Welsh to
OL,18,Ffollow the same route."
OL,20,FSome of the examples suggested include:
