OL,7,FThe Welsh Government will now look at
OL,8,Fthe recommendations before responding
OL,9,Fto the report, but First Minister
OL,10,FEluned Morgan has said: "Strengthening
OL,11,Fthe foundations of Welsh as a thriving
OL,12,Fsocial language is essential for
OL,13,Fmaintaining and increasing its use in
OL,14,Fall aspects of life. This is central
OL,15,Fto the vision of Cymraeg 2050: A
OL,16,Fmillion Welsh speakers."
