OL,7,FThe Welsh Conservatives say it is
OL,8,Fconcerning that the number of Welsh
OL,9,Fspeakers has decreased in the past two
OL,10,Fdecades and that the target for a
OL,11,Fmillion Welsh speakers by 2050 is
OL,12,F"going nowhere". They say it's
OL,13,Fessential this decline is reversed.
OL,15,FEven if the government does follow the
OL,16,Freport's recommendations, some require
OL,17,Fa need for primary legislation, so
OL,18,Fchange isn't expected to be
OL,19,Finstantaneous.
